## User Story

As a **user**, I want to **add items to my wishlist**, so that I can easily access them later.

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] **Acceptance Criteria 1**: A button should be added next to each item to add it to the wishlist.
- [ ] **Acceptance Criteria 2**: The wishlist should be viewable from the user's profile page.

## Tasks

- [ ] **Task 1**: Implement the add-to-wishlist functionality on the back-end.
- [ ] **Task 2**: Update the front-end to include a wishlist button.
- [ ] **Task 3**: Allow users to view their wishlist from the profile page.

## Additional Information

- **Priority**: Medium
- **Related Issues**: #106
- **Dependencies**: None

## Notes

Ensure the wishlist data is stored in the database for each user.
